App-ZofCMS-Plugin-FeatureSuggestionBox

The module is a plugin for App::ZofCMS that gives you a "feature suggestion
box". It is a form where a user can type up a suggestion and, once submitted,
that suggestion will arrive in your email inbox.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc App::ZofCMS::Plugin::FeatureSuggestionBox

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=App-ZofCMS-Plugin-FeatureSuggestionBox

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/App-ZofCMS-Plugin-FeatureSuggestionBox

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/App-ZofCMS-Plugin-FeatureSuggestionBox

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/App-ZofCMS-Plugin-FeatureSuggestionBox/


